Luis Suarez was handed a four-month ban for biting Italy defender Giorgio Chiellini during the World Cup . 
  His wife Sofia says that he told her he didn't bite the defender during the match . 
  She says he then admitted the truth 10 days after the incident . 
  Suarez was banned for four months after biting the Italian defender . 
  The striker joined Barcelona from Liverpool in the summer . 
 